I'm now revising the aspect ratio guidance for the LLM. The core of it involves setting a 16:9 ratio as default, as always. If the input specifies a different ratio, the LLM must follow it. I've formulated the instructions as "Default to 16:9 unless the user specifically requests something else." The objective is ensuring consistent adherence to user preferences. The simplified Chinese is not ready yet.


